Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:25.53,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur2}沉沒在拂曉之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:31.96,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur2}帶著偽造的臉龐 悄悄地靠近
